HEADWORD: directionality
<hw>directionality</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the property of a microphone
or antenna of being more sensitive to signal arriving from one direction
than from another.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> directivity.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

